name: Experiment Or Die #22
description: Yearlong project to create a new collage every day using my years of photos and personal assets. As I search through thousands of photos I come upon things I forgot I even shot and often wonder why I even did. Of course this project is the reason why even though I couldn't have known I'd be doing it even a month ago let alone 10 years ago. Power of the mind...sometimes you just know something will be, before it is. IG Nikejerk
